<section class="dc-ingredients" id="ingredients">
  <div class="dc-ingredients__inner">

    <div class="dc-ingredients__header">
      <p class="dc-eyebrow">The Science Inside</p>
      <h2 class="dc-h2">Every Ingredient Has a Reason</h2>
      <p class="dc-body-text" style="max-width: 540px; margin: 0 auto;">
        DermaCore is not a random blend. Every ingredient is selected for a specific role in supporting skin, hair, and nail health from within.*
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="dc-ingredients__image-wrap">

      {% if section.settings.ingredients_image != blank %}
        <div class="dc-ingredients__photo">
          <img
            src="{{ section.settings.ingredients_image | image_url: width: 900 }}"
            alt="DermaCore key ingredients — hydrolyzed collagen, biotin, vitamins"
            loading="lazy"
          >
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      <div class="dc-ingredients__list">

        <div class="dc-ingredient-card">
          <p class="dc-ingredient-card__name">Hydrolyzed Collagen</p>
          <p class="dc-ingredient-card__role">
            Collagen peptides are broken down for optimal absorption. Collagen is the most abundant structural protein in skin, hair, and nails — and our natural production declines from our mid-twenties.*
          </p>
          <span class="dc-ingredient-card__tag">Core Protein</span>
        </div>

        <div class="dc-ingredient-card">
          <p class="dc-ingredient-card__name">Biotin 2500mcg</p>
          <p class="dc-ingredient-card__role">
            A key B-vitamin commonly used to support healthy hair and nail growth. DermaCore delivers 2500mcg per serving — one of the most studied doses for beauty benefits.*
          </p>
          <span class="dc-ingredient-card__tag">B-Vitamin Complex</span>
        </div>

        <div class="dc-ingredient-card">
          <p class="dc-ingredient-card__name">Vitamin C · Vitamin E</p>
          <p class="dc-ingredient-card__role">
            Vitamin C supports collagen synthesis and antioxidant activity. Vitamin E (45% DV) works alongside Vitamin C to protect skin cells from environmental stressors.*
          </p>
          <span class="dc-ingredient-card__tag">Antioxidant Duo</span>
        </div>

        <div class="dc-ingredient-card">
          <p class="dc-ingredient-card__name">Folic Acid · Keratin · Zinc</p>
          <p class="dc-ingredient-card__role">
            Folic Acid supports healthy cell renewal. Keratin is a structural protein found in hair and nails. Zinc as Zinc Gluconate supports skin health and immune function.*
          </p>
          <span class="dc-ingredient-card__tag">Supporting Nutrients</span>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted);">
      *These statements have not been evaluated by the MCC or SAHPRA. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Ingredients",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "ingredients_image",
      "label": "Ingredient flat lay image",
      "info": "Upload the ingredient flat lay with the product bottle and berry/vitamin drops (image 5)"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Ingredients"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
